76
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:10,190
This is called karma.

77
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,950
Karma?

78
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,830
I can't be worse

79
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,200
than you,

80
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:16,950
