81
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:20,480
So that's what you think of me.

82
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,200
Sir,

83
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,390
we must send them out

84
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,950
in the first group leaving the city
after dawn.

85
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,680
You're the florist?

86
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,750
This is Jieyu Flower Shop?

87
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,160
Yes, Mrs. Gu.

88
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,440
What are you doing?

89
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,440
Let go of me!

90
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,320
Let go!

91
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,160
You are hiding money in the flowers
to sneak it out of city?

92
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,830
Yes, Mrs. Gu.

93
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,440
Gu Yanting,

94
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,480
where's this money going?

95
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,880
Mrs. Gu,

96
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:26,920
we're sending it to the frontlines

97
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,870
to support our comrades.

98
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,030
Him? Doing good deeds?

99
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,200
Not only that.

100
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:37,600
Mr. Gu gives all his savings

101
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,600
to the refugees.

102
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,600
He never wastes money.

103
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:44,630
Sir,

104
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:46,910
remember, you have to pamper your wife.

105
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,360
I'm not his wife!

106
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:51,840
I don't want you either.

107
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,670
With the war in chaos,

108
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,600
can you really get the money out?

109
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,840
Mr. Gu has connections.

110
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:09,120
We've been supporting the frontlines
like this for a while.

111
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:13,080
(So he's seeking treasure
to support the frontlines.)

112
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,360
(Did I misjudge him?)

113
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,110
Why are you staring?

114
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,670
You tricked me at Wangyue Theatre today.

115
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:27,240
This money is your debt.

116
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:30,000
You did the wrong thing first.

117
00:09:39,070 --> 00:09:40,030
Either way,

118
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,270
