135
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,960
You have to repay me.

136
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,840
Without the money,
I can't get the goods.

137
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,800
Mr. Paul,

138
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,150
